@startuml EditClass
|Admin|
start
:1. Open class list;
:2. Select class to edit;
:3. Open edit form with current data;
:4. Modify class details (name, schedule);
:5. Update course or schedule;
:6. Submit changes;
|ClassManagementUI|
:7. Validate new data;
|ClassController|
:8. Update class in backend;
|Database|
:9. Save updated record;
|ClassController|
:10. Return success;
|ClassManagementUI|
:11. Display confirmation;
:12. Refresh class list;
stop
@enduml
